data.body:
For some reason, my build environment started to show ambiguity between ```System.Drawing.Size``` and ```Android.Util.Size``` in ```MonoGameAndroidGameView```.

Probably something related to latest Xamarin.Android builds.

@dellis1972 @KonajuGames

```csharp
class Foo
{
     object[,] Bars1 { get; set; }
     object[,,] Bars2 { get; set; }
}
```
Does not serialize properly, even if it did, it would not find the Reader at runtime.
